                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p>on any given topic for though my back is<lb/> lamed, my tongue is loose on the proper\n                    <add>?</add>.<lb/> Only ladies have the privilege of a tongue<lb/> fastening in\n                the middle; we from miserable<lb/> masculiness must needs be <add>?</add> well\n                the<lb/> use of it in the front part. But then we may<lb/> not try it then to the\n                best advantage, even<lb/>\n                <add>?</add> arguing the ladies.</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">My writing is hardly presu<add>?</add> to a<lb/> lady; than to\n                    <add>?</add> almost straight up to make<lb/>\n                <add>?</add>, and being near sighted with all,<lb/> to not writing with spectacles,\n                than to trust<lb/> to my readiness in handling the pen to make<lb/> it figures as\n                they come without having any hope<lb/> of offering a specimen of caligraphy.</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">Remember me to your parents and <add>?</add>,<lb/> &amp; return to\n                bless <add>?</add> my best thanks for<lb/> he<add>?</add> joint kind inquiries.</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">Hoping that the course of your life<lb/> may run smooth without\n                accident or<lb/> severe trials I am</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">truly your friend</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">\n                <persName role=\"author\">Isaac Leeser</persName>\n            </p>\n            <pb n=\"Envelope\"/>\n            <p>\n                <addressee>Miss Rosa Mordecai</addressee>\n            </p>\n            <p>care of <persName>Major A. Mordecai</persName></p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">\n                <placeName>Watervliet Arsenal</placeName>\n            </p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">\n                <placeName>West Ferry</placeName>\n            </p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(2)\">\n                <placeName>New York</placeName>\n            </p>\n        </body>\n    </text>\n</TEI>"
                  },
